    <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
        Features
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        Relative Strength Index is an indicator that ranges between 0 and 100 with values outside the 30 and 70 range are of interest. This indicator is a measure of the percentage of the price move that is up compared to the total price movement. High values (above 70) indicate strong upward price movement that may not be sustainable.
